Class NullGameSoundFX

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mygdx.game.model.GameSoundFX
      • com.mygdx.game.model.NullGameSoundFX

  • public class NullGameSoundFX
extends GameSoundFX
    NullGameSoundFX is a class that serves as a null GameSoundFX, no playing any sound. It always returns null.
